Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.51,EN,,0,0,0,,I also was falling in love with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:07.65,EN,,0,0,0,,who had a really wonderfully normal, balanced, grounded life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.53,EN,,0,0,0,,and we decided together that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.89,EN,,0,0,0,,we wanted our relationship to be private
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:33.17,EN,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it is the focus on…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:39.45,EN,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, to all of us, thank you, thank you to the Amazon…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:10.39,EN,,0,0,0,,Taylor Swift! Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:36.61,EN,,0,0,0,,William Bowery Joe, as we know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:41.83,EN,,0,0,0,,and Joe plays piano beautifully and he’s always just playing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.72,EN,,0,0,0,,and making things up and kind of creating things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:49.72,EN,,0,0,0,,and as I was crazy, cause Joe has written that entire piano part
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.22,EN,,0,0,0,,and he was singing the body verse part
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.73,EN,,0,0,0,,I can see you standing, honey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.59,EN,,0,0,0,,With his arms around your body
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.39,EN,,0,0,0,,Laughing but the joke’s not funny at all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.73,EN,,0,0,0,,He was just singing it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.30,EN,,0,0,0,,the way that the whole for the first…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:13.53,EN,,0,0,0,,And, so, I was interest and asked if we could keep writing that one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.82,EN,,0,0,0,,and it was pretty obvious that it would be a duet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.03,EN,,0,0,0,,cause he has such a low voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:21.29,EN,,0,0,0,,and that’s a really good song down there in that register
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:26.32,EN,,0,0,0,,And then we were really, really big body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:44.47,EN,,0,0,0,,I just heard Joe singing the entire fully formed chorus of {\i1}Betty{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:46.63,EN,,0,0,0,,from another room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:49.02,EN,,0,0,0,,and I just was like, “hello,”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.68,EN,,0,0,0,,You’re like, “I do this professionally, and…”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.20,EN,,0,0,0,,“Hello,”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.51,EN,,0,0,0,,“and love the conversation”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.43,EN,,0,0,0,,It was a step that we will never taken
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:58.88,EN,,0,0,0,,Because why would we have ever written a song together？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.89,EN,,0,0,0,,I thought you were doing a bit like Joe and I wrote a song
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.13,EN,,0,0,0,,and I thought it gonna be like, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.40,EN,,0,0,0,,like people write 2 songs about their animals, their relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.43,EN,,0,0,0,,and you’re like, no no, it was like a real song
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.11,EN,,0,0,0,,So this was the first time that we had a conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:19.13,EN,,0,0,0,,when it came and I was like “Okay, this could be really weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.59,EN,,0,0,0,,and we could hate this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:26.55,EN,,0,0,0,,So, could we just, because…we are in quarantine and there's nothing else going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:29.31,EN,,0,0,0,,could we just try to see what was it like if we write the song together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.32,EN,,0,0,0,,So he was singing the chorus of it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.81,EN,,0,0,0,,and I thought it was not a really good sing from a man’s voice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.36,EN,,0,0,0,,from the masculine perspective
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.19,EN,,0,0,0,,and I really like that it seems to be an apology
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:32.51,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, he played me the scrabble
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:38.48,EN,,0,0,0,,I’m about to… The type game, no I can wait, I can wait
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.23,EN,,0,0,0,,It will make him sweat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.99,EN,,0,0,0,,This game, will get, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.94,EN,,0,0,0,,he will get stressed and he will,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.91,EN,,0,0,0,,“What is she playing at? What’s she gonna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.49,EN,,0,0,0,,So she’ll gonna get triple work…”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:51.66,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, which, you know, it’s not
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:06:02.75,EN,,0,0,0,,We have hidden lots of different goodies in this house
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:24.59,EN,,0,0,0,,A musical? I don’t think I'm quite up to the standard
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.32,EN,,0,0,0,,as much as I love it, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.24,EN,,0,0,0,,What's going on Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.60,EN,,0,0,0,,You’re just a happy little cat
Comment: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,--------------------TEXT-CN--------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.51,CN,,0,0,0,,我也和那个人坠入爱河
Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.51,0:00:07.65,CN,,0,0,0,,那个有着完美的、安定的、理智的生活的男人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.53,CN,,0,0,0,,并且我们一起决定
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.89,CN,,0,0,0,,我们的关系要保持私密
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.65,0:00:33.17,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候，要专注于…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.17,0:00:39.45,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候对我们来说，谢谢！谢谢亚马逊！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.48,0:01:10.39,CN,,0,0,0,,我的天哪！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.42,0:01:36.61,CN,,0,0,0,,我们都知道，William Bowery Joe (霉姐夫全名）
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.36,0:01:41.83,CN,,0,0,0,,Joe能弹一手好钢琴，而且他也经常在弹
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.72,CN,,0,0,0,,还会创作音乐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.72,0:01:49.72,CN,,0,0,0,,我真的超级激动，因为是Joe创作了整个钢琴部分
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.22,CN,,0,0,0,,而且是他唱的主歌部分
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.73,CN,,0,0,0,,我看见你站在那里，亲爱的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.59,CN,,0,0,0,,靠在他怀里
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.39,CN,,0,0,0,,应和着无聊的玩笑
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.73,CN,,0,0,0,,他就那样唱着
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.30,CN,,0,0,0,,就这样，这首歌诞生了…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.30,0:02:13.53,CN,,0,0,0,,然后呢，我就很感兴趣，问他我们能不能把这首歌创作下去
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.82,CN,,0,0,0,,当然，这明显会是一个二重唱歌曲
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.03,CN,,0,0,0,,因为Joe的声音很低
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.03,0:02:21.29,CN,,0,0,0,,这真的是一首非常惊艳的歌，尤其是那段的音域
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.55,0:02:26.32,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一个很成功的合作
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.46,0:03:44.47,CN,,0,0,0,,我还听过Joe唱Betty这首歌的完整副歌部分
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.52,0:03:46.63,CN,,0,0,0,,他的声音从另一个房间传来
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.63,0:03:49.02,CN,,0,0,0,,然后我就探个头来句：“你好呀”
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.68,CN,,0,0,0,,你来句：“我可是专业的，而且…"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.20,CN,,0,0,0,,"你好！”
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.51,CN,,0,0,0,,“我喜欢这样的对话”
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.43,CN,,0,0,0,,这是我们从未迈出的一步
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.43,0:03:58.88,CN,,0,0,0,,就是，为啥我俩要尝试一起写歌呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.89,CN,,0,0,0,,我觉得你俩那种感觉就像：我和Joe一起写歌
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.13,CN,,0,0,0,,然后我觉得那样的话，你知道
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.40,CN,,0,0,0,,俩人一起写两首，关于他们的宠物、他们的感情的歌
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.43,CN,,0,0,0,,然后你会强调，不不，这是基于现实的歌
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.11,CN,,0,0,0,,这是我们第一次关于一起写歌的交谈
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.11,0:04:19.13,CN,,0,0,0,,当这一切发生的时候，我觉得，行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.59,CN,,0,0,0,,这事可能很奇怪，我们可能会讨厌这样
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.94,0:04:26.55,CN,,0,0,0,,所以，我们能不能，因为被隔离时也没什么别的事
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.55,0:04:29.31,CN,,0,0,0,,我们能不能试一下，看看一起写歌会产生什么样的化学反应
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.32,CN,,0,0,0,,然后他就唱了副歌部分
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.81,CN,,0,0,0,,但是吧，我觉得那个部分不太适合男声
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.36,CN,,0,0,0,,就是不适合男性视角
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.19,CN,,0,0,0,,我还是很喜欢这听起来有道歉的意味
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.69,0:05:32.51,CN,,0,0,0,,嚯，这货在玩填字游戏
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.48,0:05:38.48,CN,,0,0,0,,哎呀我要…打字的游戏，不用，我可以等
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.23,CN,,0,0,0,,这会让他浑身出汗的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.99,CN,,0,0,0,,这游戏，你知道
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.94,CN,,0,0,0,,会让他压力很大，然后他就会说
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.91,CN,,0,0,0,,“她玩啥呢？她下一步要干啥？”
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.49,CN,,0,0,0,,所以她这下得做三倍的工作了“
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.24,0:05:51.66,CN,,0,0,0,,对啊， 你知道，不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.07,0:06:02.75,CN,,0,0,0,,我们在这个房子里藏了好多好东西
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.33,0:06:24.59,CN,,0,0,0,,一部音乐剧吗？我感觉我可能没到那么高的水平
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.32,CN,,0,0,0,,尽管你知道，我很喜欢音乐剧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.24,CN,,0,0,0,,怎么啦本杰明（Taylore的第四只猫猫）？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.60,CN,,0,0,0,,你就是只快乐的小猫咪
